### index
# Menampilkan semua data diskon
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discounts
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token

### show
# Menampilkan data diskon spesifik (misalnya ID 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token

### create
# Menambahkan diskon baru
POST http://localhost:8080/api/discounts
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tanggal": "2026-08-17",
    "nominal": "150000"
}

### update
# Mengubah nominal diskon (misalnya ID 1 diubah menjadi 250000)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nominal": "250000"
}

### delete
# Menghapus data diskon (misalnya ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/discounts/14
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token